{
  "title": "Guide to Using the Company MOM Module in SiteFlow",
  "metaTitle": "Guide to Using the Company MOM Module in SiteFlow",
  "metaDescription": "Create and manage Minutes of Meeting at company level in SiteFlow. Covers cross-project meetings, filters, attendee tracking, and the difference between company and project MOM.",
  "canonical": "https://siteflow.com/help/company-features/how-to-use-company-level-mom-in-SiteFlow/",
  "slug": "company-features/how-to-use-company-level-mom-in-SiteFlow",
  "category": "company-features",
  "type": "help",
  "author": "SiteFlow Operations Team",
  "publishDate": "2026-05-15T04:08:56+00:00",
  "body": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-53179\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"448\" src=\"/images/recon/Add-a-heading-52-1024x448.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-4af60d4fe1ccdf7399f8d129024b5ffd wp-block-paragraph\">Guide to using the company-level MOM module — viewing, filtering, and creating Minutes of Meeting entries that span across all projects or are not tied to any specific project.</p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Company MOM vs Project MOM</h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-fixed-layout\" style=\"border-width:2px\"><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Company-Level MOM</th><th>Project-Level MOM</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Where</td><td>Left sidebar, MOM</td><td>Inside a project, MOM tab</td></tr><tr><td>Scope</td><td>All projects or no project</td><td>That project only</td></tr><tr><td>Extra column</td><td>Project column shown</td><td>No project column needed</td></tr><tr><td>Best used for</td><td>Cross-project meetings, company-wide reviews, board meetings</td><td>Project-specific site meetings, design reviews</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Accessing Company MOM</h2>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-fd5b8352e5e63bbc010ab7b3fa1e58f9 wp-block-paragraph\">Click <strong>MOM</strong> in the left sidebar. This shows all meeting records across the company.</p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\">The MOM List</h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-fixed-layout\" style=\"border-width:2px\"><thead><tr><th>Column</th><th>What It Shows</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Name</strong></td><td>Meeting name and date</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Attendee</strong></td><td>Number of attendees</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Project</strong></td><td>Project the meeting was associated with (blank if not project-specific)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Notes</strong></td><td>Summary of what was discussed</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\">Filters</h3>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-fixed-layout\" style=\"border-width:2px\"><thead><tr><th>Filter</th><th>Options</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Search</strong></td><td>Search by meeting name</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Project</strong></td><td>Show only meetings linked to a specific project</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Date Filter</strong></td><td>All, Today, Last Week, Last Month, This Week, This Month, or Custom</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Attendee</strong></td><td>Show meetings attended by a specific person</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Creating a New MOM</h2>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-197b1314f2ff3b992530e13443851386 wp-block-paragraph\">Click <strong>New MOM +</strong> in the top right.</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-fixed-layout\" style=\"border-width:2px\"><thead><tr><th>Field</th><th>Required</th><th>What to Enter</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Date</strong></td><td>Yes</td><td>Auto-filled with today’s date</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Meeting Name</strong></td><td>Yes</td><td>A descriptive name (e.g. “Monthly Management Review”, “Cross-Project Design Meeting”)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Select Project</strong></td><td>No</td><td>Leave blank for a company-wide meeting, or select a project to associate it</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Attendee</strong></td><td>No</td><td>Search and add attendees from the company team</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Notes</strong></td><td>No</td><td>Record agenda points, decisions, and action items</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Attach Media</strong></td><td>No</td><td>Upload photos, documents, or supporting files</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-f83c6ce6d632db4970d9a2cbdefcd67a wp-block-paragraph\">Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h2>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-77818e44b9e47f105eda1d25e5cff1bd\">\n<li>Use company MOM for management-level reviews. Weekly or monthly reviews involving multiple projects should be logged here rather than inside one specific project.</li>\n<li>Leave Project blank for general meetings. Board meetings, staff training, or all-hands discussions that are not tied to any project should be saved without selecting a project.</li>\n<li>Use the Project filter to see all meetings associated with one project — including both company-level meetings linked to it and separate project-level MOM entries.</li>\n<li>Use the Attendee filter to find all meetings a specific person attended and track the action items assigned to them across the company.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">If Something Goes Wrong</h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-fixed-layout\" style=\"border-width:2px\"><thead><tr><th>Problem</th><th>Likely Cause</th><th>What to Do</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Meeting not appearing in the list</td><td>Date or Project filter is active</td><td>Reset all filters to All</td></tr><tr><td>Attendee not found in search</td><td>Person not registered in the system</td><td>Confirm the person is added as a team member in Settings, then Roles and Access</td></tr><tr><td>Meetings missing for a specific project</td><td>Company MOM shows only meetings explicitly linked to the project</td><td>Also check inside the project’s own MOM tab for project-level entries</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n"
}